<h4>Multi-cluster support for Elastic Agent</h4>

Now elastic agent can be created in different cluster based on the cluster profile. Elastic Profiles SPA is updated to reflect cluster profiles and elastic agent profiles.

<figure>
  <%= image_tag 'releases/19.3.0/elastic_profile.png', alt: 'Cluster Support' %>
</figure>

To know more about about Cluster Profiles click [here](https://docs.gocd.org/19.3.0/configuration/elastic_agents.html#concepts).

Introduced elastic agent extension v5 to support cluster profiles. For more info refer Elastic Agent Plugin Endpoint [documentation](https://plugin-api.gocd.org/19.3.0/elastic-agents/#elastic-agents).

